      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Meticulously preserved and free of any discernible wear, it represents a rare opportunity for the collector who demands an uncompromising standard of quality. This is, without reservation, a definitive specimen for the most sophisticated enthusiast.",
