    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips or swirls, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original factory protective film is still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and feature functions as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. If you are looking for a vehicle that feels and smells brand new, this is it.",
      "price": 44500.0,
