    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen remains in immaculate condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class. It is offered for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
