    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It still has that fresh interior smell and drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new showroom price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
