    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six powerplant. This specimen boasts a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-equipped limited-slip differential. The chassis is anchored by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping characteristics and roll stiffness. Meticulously maintained with zero bore scoring and a verified DME overrev report showing only minimal Stage 1 activity. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this 911 offers telepathic steering feedback and a linear torque curve that exemplifies the zenith of hydraulic-steering Porsches.",
